<td>
<th>Requirements</th>
<th>Description</th>
<tr> Name</tr>
<tr> <strong>Mandatory</strong>input field with<b>text</b>as its type. not more than <b>15</b>character long,and <b>focused</b> when page loads.
</tr>
<tr>password<strong>mandatory</strong>input field with the number of characters between 8 and 12 and starts with an alphabet and ends with a numbe
